1235
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nebreme o lokalnoj zajednici!

1236
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost i to je sve sad iskalo

1237
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:03,000
