1242
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] On dođe prezentiran!

1243
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin Pavković prvi kaže

1244
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad je tako ja riječ pravi!

1245
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:17,000
