1248
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sutra mene gospodin Pavković zovem!

1249
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa bili mogli ovako

1250
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa ljudi su rekli ne možu!

1251
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam ja tu

1252
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja nebio ako sam ti dao riješi nešto

1253
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa nema Boga ovog svijeta

1254
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] da mi daš svi ta svijeta ja nebio!

1255
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro!

1256
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prošlo sedam meseci osa!

1257
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam nigdje makao ostalo neki problemi!

1258
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ima dobio 73 MW!

1259
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Metar dokuća s ovak!

1260
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] 75 MW!

1261
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da vidite kako to izgled!

1262
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je 1000 Dulu!

1263
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da sad sve ovo...

1264
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo što vidite iz nad kuća sve dok se vidi!

1265
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ljudi šta se događa?

1266
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi kaže imamo dozdo!

1267
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao sad evo čeka se građališka

1268
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] građališka se dobije

1269
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] međutim ja vidim gdje to ide!

1270
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije smio dobiti procesiju on je dobio!

1271
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije imao pravo snažu on dobio!

1272
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek je blizak pa dovoljno je samo malo se raspitati!

1273
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zna se iz koje je to pugovalo!

1274
00:44:14,000 --> 00:44:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I da se ne lažemo!

1275
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam svobodan čovjek!

1276
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Educirao sam se!

1277
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu pričati šta hoću!

1278
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zahvalo me tako!

1279
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I danas sam ostio potrebu

1280
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] što moralno i duhovno

1281
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] da vama prenesem ono što znam!

1282
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ako treba ostavit ću broj!

1283
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imam sve dozvole, papire, šta rade i kako rade!

1284
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da vam pomogne!

1285
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta god treba!

1286
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A neću vam mojiti šta ćete vi raditi!

1287
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi doneste sami su!

1288
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo je vaša mjesna zdajnice, raditi šta!

1289
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pođem u Istru,

1290
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] zvoni mi telefon četiri dana!

1291
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam ljepak uzmo stara sedam mjeseci!

1292
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mario šta je ovo dva bagera u Miljkovića?

1293
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja držim dok sam ovo tamo vam!

1294
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi mi se, da oprostite, pokvarišaj mi put!

1295
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebao sam nešto u Istru, neki posao radi!

1296
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je, kako je stane modelnicama?

1297
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zovem Hlakovića!

1298
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je tu malo povišenih tonova!

1299
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni gospodin Hlaković kaže:

1300
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to prodao, meni mi niste dali prada!

1301
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Ivane, nije to rješenje, dragi!

1302
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to?

1303
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kome je se prodao?

1304
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako smo se malo porečkali?

1305
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da se mu kaže u malo boljim odnosima,

1306
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] rekao:

1307
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ja ne mogu pogledat tuč!

1308
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo malo!

1309
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] To ćemo mi sve gledati!

1310
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I normalno i malo komedi proradi!

1311
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to, ja vam ne mogu pričati!

1312
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su nasilu, počeli praviti bagera dva unište dnevno dum!

1313
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tuci kamen!

1314
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin Hlaković je govorio da će za mjesec dana poradnati!

1315
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Četiri mjeseca su oni ravnali gore!

1316
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Krš, kamen, treba tuvić, to sve poradnati!

1317
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sto duluba!

1318
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nema koga nisam pituo!

1319
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Istraživački sam, evo, bavio s ovim temama!

1320
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zdravko namiča, evo, ne!

1321
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjeka sam se sastoo isključivo da pitam iz tih koga,

1322
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali neko zna ko stoji iza profesora u Mostaru,

1323
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji jutri je ratar i niste na auto,

1324
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] on odjednom investitor!

1325
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nismo godali!

1326
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I drž veda, i kad dođe, kako kažu,

1327
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ko traži, i otvori se!

1328
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dođe, dobijem ja, ove, kako se zove,

1329
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] notarski ugovor, dobijem Trna bio!

1330
00:46:18,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospoda su prodali preko ERS-a,

1331
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] ruskoj kompaniji.

1332
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite, vi sad pramote u Mostelu,

1333
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] dva mladića su 20 godina poginu,

1334
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] da neko vrdo proda,

1335
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] na 30 godina, ruskoj kompaniji, koji je na Trnavisti.

1336
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, maša, maša, maša, maša,

1337
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja da uprave je!

1338
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo malo!

1339
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo cikrema ne ti kaže!

1340
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što gospoda radi,

1341
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] oni radi za papire,

1342
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] deset kuta će će raditi samo na papirima,

1343
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne na solarima.

1344
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nisu uopći, oni su samo posrednici da rješaju dozvole.

1345
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Profesor u Mostaviji je uzao 5% samo da sređuje dozvole.

1346
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] 90% je kapital,

1347
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rusi, Kinezi,

1348
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] u Stooticu u Brdo prodali Kineziju.

1349
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čini je tu?

1350
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Udakle nekom pravo da proda Brdo,

1351
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bavo bi trebao da proda.

1352
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je li živi neko iza nas?

1353
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li će neko živiti iza nas?

1354
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] To nema države Flajda.

1355
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu se koriste...

1356
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo malo.

1357
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo malo.

1358
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta kako u ugovorima ovaj probacij,

1359
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] 2,7 ili ona samo na papirima,

1360
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] da se to može prati.

1361
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] 900 milijada što je papire izganio.

1362
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, nego gospodine kako je svare,

1363
00:47:32,000 --> 00:47:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako je zaradio?

1364
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ja ga gledam moć,

1365
00:47:34,000 --> 00:47:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne kaže ovdje kako je zaradio.

1366
00:47:35,000 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne kaže svako.

1367
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kaže svako.

1368
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Stooticu su prodali.

1369
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prodali su već.

1370
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa gospodine, pa gospodine izvište Riva,

1371
00:47:45,000 --> 00:47:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako je da vas uože.

1372
00:47:46,000 --> 00:47:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Recite kome za koga radite,

1373
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] za Rusi, Kinezi, za Ove.

1374
00:47:50,000 --> 00:47:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste samo tihnih pralotnje,

1375
00:47:52,000 --> 00:47:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] i čak radite dozvoda da se odbavate.

1376
00:47:54,000 --> 00:47:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi govori kako je zvazni ljubi učušenom.

1377
00:47:57,000 --> 00:47:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Bogu ga je svega došna.

1378
00:47:59,000 --> 00:48:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ih imao za ovo.

1379
00:48:00,000 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moćete to raditi.

1380
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ste i kraje svijeta.

1381
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:05,000
[SPEAKER_09] Mislim da nema više potrebe.

1382
00:48:05,000 --> 00:48:07,000
[SPEAKER_09] Možete.

1383
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:24,000
[SPEAKER_06] Evo, ja ću reći sad.

1384
00:48:24,000 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, ja sam jedan od potencijalnih investitela.

1385
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:29,000
[SPEAKER_06] nismo još nisu još završili.

1386
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:31,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, ako narod kaže gdje se pravi, gdje se pravi.

1387
00:48:31,000 --> 00:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_06] A ovom gospodine će odšli da se obratimo.

1388
00:48:35,000 --> 00:48:39,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, vi pitate za koga vi radite, za Rusi, za Kineze.

1389
00:48:39,000 --> 00:48:43,000
[SPEAKER_06] Za koga ja radim, za Rusi, za Kineze.

1390
00:48:43,000 --> 00:48:46,000
[SPEAKER_06] ti ništa ne radiš, ko što si ima u propastrasi.

1391
00:48:46,000 --> 00:48:48,000
[SPEAKER_06] Ne moj molim da se inicijetivovići.

1392
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:49,000
[SPEAKER_06] Više ne.

1393
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:50,000
[SPEAKER_06] Koji je broj jedan?

1394
00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:51,000
[SPEAKER_06] Broj dva znači.

1395
00:48:51,000 --> 00:48:53,000
[SPEAKER_06] Potencijalni investitela znači i tražnost može.

1396
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:57,000
[SPEAKER_06] i ušte planije koncesiju, ako se može dobiti za pravi solare.

1397
00:48:57,000 --> 00:49:01,000
[SPEAKER_06] Zato što tamo, zato što se planije Jetropark, pa bi tu bio trakostancija.

1398
00:49:01,000 --> 00:49:03,000
[SPEAKER_06] Za tu jedino možete pomoćati drugo, ništa ne može.

1399
00:49:03,000 --> 00:49:04,000
[SPEAKER_06] Neće se biti.

1400
00:49:04,000 --> 00:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_06] U redu, ti kao još neće, neće.

1401
00:49:07,000 --> 00:49:08,000
[SPEAKER_06] Neće se.

1402
00:49:08,000 --> 00:49:10,000
[SPEAKER_06] Zato si nama govorio, neće se.

1403
00:49:10,000 --> 00:49:14,000
[SPEAKER_06] Molim te, vrataš ti tamo ove mjesta znači, nekaj.

1404
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:16,000
[SPEAKER_06] Neka je, ali ima pravi to.

1405
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, nekaj ali ne smije, jer da li ja priznam.

1406
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, tražili smo koncesiju.

1407
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:24,000
[SPEAKER_06] Normalno, u svaku konsulticiju traži koncesiju,

1408
00:49:24,000 --> 00:49:27,000
[SPEAKER_06] a pošelje se zahtje, pak općina u Županije odobri.

1409
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:32,000
[SPEAKER_06] Zakonski je, od koncesije, od proizvodnje 2,5% ide u Županiji,

1410
00:49:32,000 --> 00:49:35,000
[SPEAKER_06] od moga pola ide općine pola Županije.

1411
00:49:35,000 --> 00:49:37,000
[SPEAKER_06] To je zakonski, od proizvodnje.

1412
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:41,000
[SPEAKER_06] Mi smo konusi još 1,25% direktor mjestove zajednice.

1413
00:49:41,000 --> 00:49:45,000
[SPEAKER_06] Znači, po nekakvim pronačunima to bilo prilike, godišnje 350.000 mar.

1414
